title: Spacious Edgewater Condo w Washer and Dryer
posting_body: ['SPACIOUS 2 bdrm, 1 bath, CONDO FOR RENT On corner of Lake Ave and W. 110th St.', 'In suite private laundry/dryer', 'Large living room and large bedroom.', '900 sq.', 'ft. total Lots of storage space including attic.', "Unit located on the 2nd floor of a small 2-story Condominium Building Surrounded by mansions in a beautiful neighborhood Neutrally decorated and clean Central Heating and Air-conditioning Electric Range, Refrigerator, and Dishwasher Walking distance to Lake Erie and Edgewater Park/Beach Walking distance to: CVS, Starbucks, Chipotle, Lucky's Supermarket, Clifton Mini Mart, Anytime Fitness, Liquid Planet, Twist, several banks, several restaurants, pizzeria, diners, hair and beauty salons, barbershop, tanning, kindergarten, etc Close to Shoreway (OH-2) Only 5 minutes by car from Downtown life and sports events Frequent and fast public transportation (10 min ride) to Downtown 5 minutes to: Target, 24h Giant Eagle, Marc's, Aldi, Home Depot and Lakewood bars", 'One reserved parking spot.', 'Guest parking also available.', 'New laminate floors.', 'Sorry no pets']
